 i prób wyjaśnienia nieporozumienia oraz niedorzeczność życia w bazie, która jest skupiskiem dziwnych i nieprzystosowanych ludzi.","popularity":0.5588,"poster_path":"/kAruqIkf1GxYyWS03pq7NKdp6dC.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-06","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":4.6,"vote_count":26,"credit_id":"66fb36ecf2b9c97c1dd61e2b","department":"Production","job":"Executive Producer"},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[18],"id":1426215,"title":"Angels in the Asylum","original_language":"en","original_title":"Angels in the Asylum","overview":"","popularity":0.3104,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":0.0,"vote_count":0,"credit_id":"679b56100902b69ec7fbca65","department":"Production","job":"Executive Producer"},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/S15LGYPZWTj1h1hyvfPXopzVKJ.jpg","genre_ids":[35,18],"id":1470465,"title":"Przyjaciel Dorothy","original_language":"en","original_title":"A Friend of Dorothy","overview":"Dorothy jest samotną wdową. Choć ciało odmawia jej posłuszeństwa, umysł wciąż ma ostry jak brzytwa. Jej codzienną rutynę – leki, suszone śliwki i krzyżówki – wywraca do góry nogami 17-letni JJ, który przypadkiem wkopuje piłkę do jej ogrodu. Tak rodzi się niezwykła przyjaźń. Choć pochodzą z dwóch różnych światów, odkrywają, że łączy ich więcej, niż mogliby przypuszczać.","popularity":0.3598,"poster_path":"/5YjFZoCfBJ2G40SHPa5CFy60jdC.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-01","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.1,"vote_count":30,"credit_id":"68f7645b6173dc05e53a3980","department":"Production","job":"Executive Producer"},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[878,18,9648],"id":1633210,"title":"Stranger Things: The First Shadow","original_language":"en","original_title":"Stranger Things: The First Shadow","overview":"","popularity":0.3449,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":0.0,"vote_count":0,"credit_id":"698c48f1303faa277cd54389","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/374JDqWrtG97dHQj64DMD7cOjYH.jpg","genre_ids":[99,36],"id":1013569,"title":"A Cooler Climate","original_language":"en","original_title":"A Cooler Climate","overview":"","popularity":0.2785,"poster_path":"/oTO3o6ZPxnSFGv98TmaxWoPp7dV.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-07","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":8.0,"vote_count":3,"credit_id":"6a0ec0b8d047e4b6cae2bf99","department":"Crew","job":"Thanks"}],"id":468}